def: A material found in the cell walls of cork. It is amodification of lignin.
A division of vermiform gastropod mollusks, without a shell,belonging to the Isopleura.
An apple roasted till black, to be served in a dish of boiledcustard.
The process of restoring a cheek which has been destroyedwholly or in part.
Having a tendency by nature; prone; proclivous. [R.] Mrs.Browning.
